maple: with(numtheory);knodel:= proc(i,k)local a,n,ok;for n from k+1 to i do  ok:=1;  for a from 1 to n do    if gcd(a,n)=1 then if (a&^(n-k) mod n)<>1 then ok:=0; break fi fi  od;  if ok=1 then print(n); fi;od;end:knodel(1000,5); # _Paolo P. Lava_, Feb 24 2012
